de.awi.floenavigation.synchronization

Class SampleMeasurement

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.awi.floenavigation.synchronization.SampleMeasurement

  • public class SampleMeasurement
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates a Sample Measurement object with getters and setters for all the parameters of a DatabaseHelper.sampleMeasurementTable Table in Database. Used by SampleMeasurementSync to create a new Sample Measurement Object to be inserted into the Database.
    See Also:
    SyncActivity, SampleMeasurementSync, de.awi.floenavigation.synchronization
